==English==
===Pronunciation===
(US) IPA: /fəˈniːʃən/
===Alternative spellings===
*[[Phœnician]]

===Noun===
'''Phoenician'''
# a native or inhabitant of [[Phoenicia]], a country on the eastern shores of the [[Mediterranean Sea]] in around 1000 BC.
# the [[semitic]] language spoken by the inhabitants of Phoenicia.

===Adjective===
'''Phoenician'''
# of or related to the country or [[civilisation]] of Phoenicia.

